---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Lead from "../../components/Lead.astro";
import NextSteps from "../../components/NextSteps.astro";
import { url } from "../../lib/url";
---

<Base
  title="Not medical advice — and crisis resources"
  description="This site is educational, not medical advice. If you're in crisis, here's where to get help right now."
  crumbs={[]}
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">Not medical advice</h1>
  <Lead>
    Everything here is educational — one person sharing what he's learned and
    found helpful. It isn't medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment, and it's
    not a substitute for a qualified professional who knows your situation.
  </Lead>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      Nervous-system and trauma work can stir things up. If a practice ever
      makes you feel worse, it's completely okay to stop — opening your eyes,
      looking around the room, standing up, or reaching out to someone are all
      valid responses. Nothing here is required, and slower is always allowed.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're dealing with significant distress, please consider working with
      a licensed, trauma-informed professional. This site is not designed for
      people in crisis.
    </p>

    <h2>If you're in crisis right now</h2>
    <p>You deserve support, and it's available.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>US — call or text 988</strong> (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline),
        any time, free and confidential.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>US — text HOME to 741741</strong> (Crisis Text Line).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Emergencies — call 911</strong> (or your local emergency
        number).
      </li>
      <li>
        Outside the US, <a
          href="https://findahelpline.com/"
          rel="noopener">findahelpline.com</a
        > lists free crisis lines by country.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <NextSteps>
    <li><a href={url("modalities/")}>Find a practitioner</a></li>
    <li><a href={url("practices/")}>Gentle practices</a></li>
    <li><a href={url("")}>Back home</a></li>
  </NextSteps>
</Base>
